# New Project Day1 Checklist / 新项目 Day1 启动清单

When starting a new repo, execute this checklist first.
新仓库启动时，先完整执行此清单。

## 1) Foundation / 基础设施

- Initialize monorepo structure (`apps/`, `packages/`, workspace config).
- Pin runtime/package manager versions (`.nvmrc`, `engines`, pnpm version).
- Add `.gitignore` for build/cache/artifacts.

## 2) CI Baseline / CI 基线

- Create pipeline with required gates: `lint`, `type-check`, `test`, `build`.
- Ensure generated artifacts step exists when needed (e.g., Prisma generate).
- Run CI once and record run URL as baseline evidence.

## 3) Rule System / 规则体系

- Add strict global workflow rule (default execute + DoD + blocker handling).
- Add stack-aware rules for frontend/backend/monorepo by globs.
- Add reusable kickoff prompt template for future sessions.

## 4) Delivery Board / 交付看板

- Create `todo.md` with sections:
  - milestones
  - timestamped completion log
  - risk ledger
  - external blockers
  - release readiness checklist
- Every completed task must include timestamp and evidence.

## 5) Local Verification / 本地验证

- Add one-command smoke script for core path.
- Add rollback script or rollback runbook.
- Verify all checks locally before first feature wave.

## 6) Definition of Ready to Build / 开发开工门禁

Proceed to feature development only when all items below are true:
仅当以下全部满足才进入功能开发：

- CI baseline is green.
- Rules are in place.
- Todo board is initialized.
- Smoke path is runnable.
- Rollback path is documented.
